                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Mediocre but regular.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red (vivid scarlet)</seg>
                        <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11077Zadengel">Za-Dǝngǝl</persName> is
                        mentioned as the scribe in Additio 1 (he appears as the scribe in some other
                        Mss., e.g., MY-019, AQG-002, MR-040).
                        <date>First half of the 19th
                           century.</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ፍ፡</abbr> for <expan>ፍቱሐ፡ </expan> (e.g., <locus target="#36ra">36ra</locus>, 36vb, 39ra)</item>
